{"word":"G678 - ἀπροσωπολήπτως - aprosōpolḗptōs - ap-ros-o-pol-ape'-tos - Without respect of persons","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπροσωπολήπτως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aprosōpolḗptōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ros-o-pol-ape'-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without respect of persons</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பட்சபாதமில்லாமல் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"without respect of persons impartially"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a compound of <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of a presumed compound of <a href=\"#/G4383 - πρόσωπον - prósōpon - pros'-o-pon/4383\">G4383</a> and <a href=\"#/G2983 - λαμβάνω - lambánō - lam-ban'-o/2983\">G2983</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G4381 - προσωπολήπτης - prosōpolḗptēs - pros-o-pol-ape'-tace/4381\">G4381</a>); in a way <i>not accepting</i> the <i>person</i>, that is, <i>impartially:</i> - without respect of persons.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2146/2146\">G2146</a>, <a href=\"#/G4380/4380\">G4380</a>, <a href=\"#/G4381/4381\">G4381</a>, <a href=\"#/G4382/4382\">G4382</a>, <a href=\"#/G4383/4383\">G4383</a>, <a href=\"#/G678/678\">G678</a>"}]}